================================================================================================

This section provides safe user management capabilities including:
- Transferring object ownership before dropping users
- Using nz_change_owner utility for bulk ownership transfer
- Dry-run mode to preview changes
- Safety checks and validation

User Management Options:
1. Drop user with automatic ownership transfer
2. View user's owned objects
3. Transfer ownership only (no user drop)
4. List all database users
5. Check user permissions and grants
6. Return to main menu

Choose user management option (1-6): 3

--- Transfer Object Ownership ---
Enter source username (FROM): USG75
Enter target username (TO): FCBORPHAN

Objects that will be transferred from USG75 to FCBORPHAN:
  - Tables:  (across all databases)
  - Views:  (across all databases)
  - Sequences:  (across all databases)
  - Total: 0

Continue with ownership transfer? (y/n): y

